                    CALL FOR PAPER AND PROPOSALS FOR TUTORIAL


             ******************************************************
                                     IEEE
                       ENGINEERING MANAGEMENT CONFERENCE
                        "Global Engineering Management:
                        Emerging Trends in Asia Pacific"
             ******************************************************

                                 Sponsored by:
               		  IEEE EMS Chapter Singapore
			         IES Singapore

                               June 28-30, 1995
                         Pan Pacific Hotel, Singapore


The IEEE Engineering Management Conference is an annual Conference of the
Engineering Management Society, Institute of Electrical & Electronics
Engineers (USA).

Major topics include but not limited to :
 * Cross-Cultural Engineering Management
 * Networked Enterprise
 * Engineering Quality and Productivity
 * Process Re-engineering
 * Global Information Systems
 * Product Development and Innovation
 * Impact of Client/Server Computing
 * Research and Development Management
 * International Project Management
 * Regional and Global Technology Transfer
 * Manufacturing Strategies
 * Strategies for Asian Brand Products

Authors are requested to send extended summaries (Maximum four (4) A4-sized
pages) to:

